{"tid":289311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠向DSE生派$5,000　擴至屯門","createTime":"2017-06-19T01:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T01:48:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa6120df6a601f8f92023318ba2f9ac24e3eb1c1","tid":289311,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T01:23:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20060871&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170619\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20060871%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170619&d=qCyVfIZAWkoOQgf583wEdsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=8622876b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20060871%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170619&h=f7c4eda9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20060871&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170619</a><br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠向DSE生派$5,000　擴至屯門<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】李嘉誠基金會繼上年度向天水圍及離島區中學DSE考生派發5,000元現金「善用錢」，昨公佈擴大計劃，明年起向屯門DSE考生每人派5,000元現金，料有逾4,000名屯門學生受惠。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠<br />\n<br />\n逾萬學生受惠<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠基金會昨公佈，「善用錢」計劃獲社會支持，讓學生自行決定5,000元的用途具多重意義，亦收到很多學校、家長、地區人士意見，望計劃擴展至屯門區中學。基金會在鼓勵同學「善用自主、善用金錢」下，宣佈2018年起擴展至屯門區。連同天水圍及離島區，預計明年共91間學校，逾一萬名學生受惠；翻查資料，屯門區下屆DSE學生約有4,300人。<br />\n基金會又指，早前向逾5,700名善用錢申請者進行問卷調查。在回收的4,244問卷中，約七成同學會將現金用於教學相關用途，如DSE考試費、留位費、購買練習、補習等。<br />\n裘錦秋中學（屯門）校長許振隆稱，屯門較多基層學童，5,000元現金能幫助部份學生，「試過有個學生要去維園攞獎，都因為太遠同交通費貴唔敢去，最尾老師帶佢出去維園，個學生之前冇去過港島，仲好驚訝公園原來可以咁大」。<br />\n■記者葉偉東<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=qCyVfIZAWkoOQgf583wEdsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=85fb2e11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼"},{"pid":"79baad95312db99880c59050c56fe63d63723005","tid":289311,"uid":760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T01:36:47.000Z","msg":"就考dse未岀過港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac98cd5c4d3010249bfa4cf3ea29b1a562033c3","tid":289311,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T01:47:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b38d9cd2086832b19ca2696722b19d93e9161203","tid":289311,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T01:48:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"becf9d57bda851ced1bc6328838b8abdc178637e","tid":289311,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T01:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就考dse未岀過港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為交通費唔敢去維園"}]}